FILE 7: /home/vasu-hdd/yocto-gateway-rt/layers/meta-cclrte/conf/machine/rpi4-cclrte.conf

Machine config for RPi4 with PREEMPT_RT for motion control.
require conf/machine/raspberrypi4-64.conf
PREFERRED_PROVIDER_virtual/kernel = "linux-raspberrypi"
LINUX_VERSION_EXTENSION = "-cclrte-rt"
MACHINE_EXTRA_RRECOMMENDS += " kernel-modules"
MACHINE_FEATURES:append = " rtc"

Kernel cmdline for motion control RT:
CMDLINE:append = " isolcpus=2,3 nohz_full=2,3 rcu_nocbs=2,3 threadirqs preempt=full nosoftlockup"

RPI config: GPU_MEM=16, ENABLE_UART=1, ENABLE_SPI_BUS=1, ENABLE_I2C=1, force_turbo=1 via RPI_EXTRA_CONFIG (also arm_freq=1800, arm_freq_min=1800, over_voltage=2, disable_splash=1, dtoverlay=disable-bt to free UART for RS485, enable watchdog via dtparam=watchdog=on)

IMAGE_FSTYPES = "rpi-sdimg wic.bz2"

